ABOUT
 With this module, FusionInventory can accept OCS Inventory software
 deployment order.
 With this module, the agent is also able to do peer to peer file
 exchange with the other FusionInventory Agent.

 If the P2P option is turned on, the agent will looks for peer in its network. The network size will be limited at 255 machines.
 P2P feature and its dependencies (POE) are optional.

SECURITY NOTE
 You must use HTTPS communication between the agent and the server

